window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What happens in the wake of </b><b><i>Failure Mode</i></b><b>?</b></p> <p>The <i>Aftermath</i> of a stunning victory—especially an unexpected, complete, and final victory—should be high-fives all around, listening to politicians give boring congratulatory speeches, and a well-deserved rest for the Merry Band of Pirates. Yes, the galaxy is still a freakin' mess, but that is nothing new, and for a change, that can be someone else's problem.</p> <p>Until, you know, something really bad happens, and only the Pirates can deal with the problem... Or not.</p>"; 
